data.description:
Come home to this charming property nestled in the heart of The Arbors community in Pooler, GA! This beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch-style home is your key to stylish, comfortable living. 

You are greeted by an open-concept layout bathed in natural light. The spacious living room seamlessly flows into the spacious kitchen. The primary bedroom is a tranquil retreat, featuring a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom. Two additional bedrooms provide ample space for family, guests, or a home office. 

Step outside to your large privacy-fenced backyard, perfect for entertaining or relaxing under the pergola. With a two-car garage and easy access to everything the beautiful Pooler Community has to offer!
